	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Genesis homebrew scene has really low activity. Although it is much easier to program for Genesis than for any 8-bit console, expectations and requirements for the art, design, etc is equally higher, and there aren't much artists and designers with needed skills among the enthusiasts.
<br />
<br />The main place for a Genesis dev is <a href="http://gendev.spritesmind.net/forum/" class="postlink">SpritesMind forum</a>, and if you prefer to use Basic, there is <a href="http://devster.proboards.com" class="postlink">Devster forums</a> as well.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


